  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"THIS IS KIKO\"</strong> is an adventure game set in the modern era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486630/extras/07e80cf4934277f08f408570dc6b7995.avif?t=1761521222\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long time ago, my younger sister and I lived together in a house by the sea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day, I worked and scavenged through trash to find things we could use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our parents had left us, but we were doing just fine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And then, one day… I remember meeting <i>her</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Was she a good person? I should have asked myself that question sooner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But even now, I can’t forget the memory of that <i>fire cooking the meat</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486630/extras/26a5f26acbb1f8a93a7bb6da7ebda5a0.avif?t=1761521222\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A walking simulator where various events unfold as you explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate objects to progress through the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No quest markers or time limits—play at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>She</i> is right, and <i>she</i> is wrong.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong> 15–50 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming is allowed without permission, whether for personal or commercial use.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"THIS IS KIKO\"</strong> is an adventure game set in the modern era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486630/extras/07e80cf4934277f08f408570dc6b7995.avif?t=1761521222\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long time ago, my younger sister and I lived together in a house by the sea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day, I worked and scavenged through trash to find things we could use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our parents had left us, but we were doing just fine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And then, one day… I remember meeting <i>her</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Was she a good person? I should have asked myself that question sooner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But even now, I can’t forget the memory of that <i>fire cooking the meat</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486630/extras/26a5f26acbb1f8a93a7bb6da7ebda5a0.avif?t=1761521222\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A walking simulator where various events unfold as you explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate objects to progress through the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No quest markers or time limits—play at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>She</i> is right, and <i>she</i> is wrong.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong> 15–50 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming is allowed without permission, whether for personal or commercial use.</p></li></ul>",
